<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.7.3">
<l>tūyāṉait tūya maṟaiyāṉai teṉṉāli</l>
<l>mēyāṉai mēvā ḷuyiruṇ ṭamutuṇṭa</l>
<l>vāyāṉai mālai vaṇaṅki yavaṉperumai</l>
<l>pēcātār pēcceṉṟum pēccalla kēṭṭāmē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The speech of those who do not speak of his eminence,</l>
<l rend="indent">worshiping Māl, the pure one,</l>
<l>The one of the pure Vedas, the one who dwells in southern Āli,</l>
<l>The one whose mouth sucked the milk, sucking away the life of [his] enemy,</l>
<l>Is never speech; [this] we have heard.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
